	<h1 class="title">从《金融时报》到《纽约时报》，她的时尚报道不一样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-14 11:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23787/medium/23787.jpeg?1457776534" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


